<br>
I have fairly low AC and haven't hit 200 Wis yet, and I'm level 52. I'm not exactly sure what other stats matter for a druid, but I've found that I'm overweight a lot. The str buff isn't that great because if it wears off while I'm quadkiting (maybe before I snare them all) then I'm dead. It'd be great if you could all advise me on what to upgrade to and how to get it. Thnx!<br>
<br>
Head - Leatherfoot Raider's Cap: 7AC +5Str +5Agi +10Cha +5vsMagic<br>
Face - Silver Ruby Veil: +4Str +4Wis<br>
Neck - Black Iron Medallion: +3Wis +3Int (working on Rough Silver Chain)<br>
Ear 1 - Gold Jasper Earring: +3Wis<br>
Ear 2 - Gold Jasper Earring: +3Wis<br>
<br>
Shoulders - Braided Ivy Cords: 4ac +5Wis<br>
Back - Kunzar Cloak: 7AC +2Wis +2Int +10vsFire <br>
Chest - Ulthork Hide Tunic: 13AC +3Wis -5Cha -35HP +35Mana <br>
Arms - Elder Spiritist Vambracers: 8AC (Effect: Drones of Doom)<br>
Wrist 1 - Chipped Bone Bracelet: 4AC +5Wis<br>
Wrist 2 - Chipped Bone Bracelet: 4AC +5Wis<br>
Hands - Split Paw Hide Gloves: 4AC +3Dex +2Wis <br>
Finger 1 - Platinum Jasper Ring: +6Wis<br>
Finger 2 - Platinum Jasper Ring: +6Wis<br>
Waist - Straw Spun Belt: 10AC<br>
Legs - Vermiculated Leggings: 8AC +3Str +5Wis +7vsPoison <br>
Feet - Acolyte's Anklet: 3AC +2Agi +2Wis +3Cha <br>
<br>
Primary - Paw of Opolla: 9AC +5Sta +9Agi +9Wis -5Cha -5vsDisease +5Mana <br>
Secondary - Testament of Vanear: +10Wis +10Mana<br>
Ranged - Small Resisting Deity: +2Cha +2vsMagic +2vsDisease <br>
<br>
Resist Gear:<br>
Bone Talisman: +4Wis +10vsMagic<br>
Drakescale Belt: 5AC +3Dex +10vsFire<br>
Crown of the Froglok Kings: 12AC +20vsFire +20vsCold<br>
Cloak of the Ice Bear: 8AC +20vsCold +10HP <br>
<br>
Backpacks:<br>
Hand Made Backpack: 10slot 10%reduce<br>
<br>
-Moro<br>
52nd Druid of Vazaelle<br>
