<br>
Head:  Crown of the Froglok Kings 12AC and great resists<br>
<br>
Ears: 2 Forest Loops - same Wis and 2AC each (about 400PP  each on Veeshan but you can quad giants in FM til you get em)<br>
<br>
Face:  Replace Silver Ruby Veil with Plat Ruby Veil - +7 str, +7 wis).  Should be pretty cheap these days with Velious jewelry on market.<br>
<br>
Neck:  Replace BIM with Chrysoberyl Talisman, 5AC +3 wis +20 mana - dropped by Mino Elder in Lguk.  500-1kPP or help a monk kill Raster in exchange for the Talisman.<br>
<br>
Shoulders:  Replace Cords with Tattered Mantle - 12AC.  Drops off of Gullerback in BW.  You can't solo him but he is always being killed since he is PH for the wurmslayer dragons and the mantle is Lore and rots a lot.<br>
<br>
Chest:  Dunno what race you are, but if you are a WE, Half elf or human, replace ulthork tunic with Treeweave.  Drops off Gorgul Paclok in BW (named Giant) - 25AC +10 str.  You can and should be hunting at the giant fort (grouped) for exp anyway, and you can track and pull Gorgul for the group.<br>
<br>
Back:  At 52 you can camp the elusive mammoth cloak - 7AC +4 wis - drops off the Alchemist in Permafrots.  getting the camp, and then staying awake, is the hard part.  Very rare drop or 2000PP.<br>
<br>
Feet:  Well, you can always organize an Efreeti raid and hope the GEBs drop.  Otherwise they are running 7k on Veeshan.<br>
<br>
Secondary:  Ditch the Testament - the 0AC is a killer.  Get a Charred Guardian Shield - 600PP max - 9AC and +9 wis.<br>
<br>
Range:  Learn the Frontier Mountain rare cycle and try for a Medicine Totem from Blugtigin - think it's 6AC and +5 wis (or vice versa LOL).  Rare but doable, and you will get other items to sell for plat to buy some of the other things listed above.<br>
<br>
You may sacrifice a little wis with thgese items but the AC boost will more than justify it.<br>
<br>
Amarin Crystalthorn<br>
Level 55 Preserver<br>
Lost Order of Akalabeth<br>
Veeshan<br>
<br>
<br>
